description: This file defines the interface for a VLAN Manager plugin in the COSA library. It includes function declarations for initializing, checking object support, and unloading the VLAN manager component, along with macro definitions and license information.

methods.name: VlanManager_Init
methods.description: Initializes the VLAN Manager with a maximum version supported and plugin info.

methods.name: VlanManager_IsObjectSupported
methods.description: Checks if a specific object name is supported by the VLAN Manager.

methods.name: VlanManager_Unload
methods.description: Unloads or cleans up the VLAN Manager plugin.
